    "en": {
      "title": "Overseas postal charges increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Department of Postal says that the revision of foreign postal charges will be increased from today (1).",
        "Deputy Post-master Rajitha Ranasinghe said the current international postal charges are based on 2018 dollar rate, adding that the charges are being revised since the dollar rate has risen sharply at present.",
        "He said that international registered postal charges will also be revised from today."
      ],
